  "text": "In this study, the width of the geotextile mattress of the GMSP is selected based on the suggestions of Xie and Liu [CITATION_1] . The width of mattress on the upstream side (L u ) is 3 cm and the width on the leeside (L d ) is 4 cm (see Fig 7) , i.e. the mattress covers a range from x = -0.03 m to 0.04 m (x = the distance to the anchoring point of the sloping plate, see Fig 8) . The averaged seepage hydraulic gradient beneath the mattress i m is calculated as:",
